sce <- readRDS("/mnt/nmorais-nfs/marta/pA_karine/r_session/e12h-preliminary-analysis/integration/data/sce-total.rds")
norm_mat <- (2**assays(sce)$limma)-1
ln_mat <- log(norm_mat + 1)
ln_mat[1:5]
## [1] -0.0622657399  0.0002646264  0.0024995997  0.0002107460  0.0001254542
srt <- CreateSeuratObject(counts = ln_mat, min.cells = 0, min.features = 0)
srt <- FindVariableFeatures(srt, selection.method = "vst", nfeatures = 4000)
# Identify the 20 most highly variable genes
top20 <- head(VariableFeatures(srt), 20)

# plot variable features with and without labels
plot1 <- VariableFeaturePlot(srt)
plot2 <- LabelPoints(plot = plot1, points = top20, repel = TRUE)
## When using repel, set xnudge and ynudge to 0 for optimal results
plot2

all.genes <- rownames(srt)
srt <- ScaleData(srt, features = all.genes)
## Centering and scaling data matrix
srt <- RunPCA(srt, features = VariableFeatures(object = srt), npcs = 100)

ElbowPlot(srt, ndims = 100) + 
  geom_vline(xintercept = 25, color = "red", alpha = 0.5) + 
  theme(text = element_text(size = 10), 
        axis.text.x = element_text(size = 10),
        axis.text.y = element_text(size = 10))

srt <- RunTSNE(srt,
             dim.embed = 3,
            dims = 1:25)
srt <- FindNeighbors(srt, 
                     reduction = "pca", 
                     dims = seq_len(25),
                     compute.SNN = TRUE)
## Computing nearest neighbor graph
## Computing SNN
srt <- FindClusters(srt, 
                        resolution = seq(0.1, 2, 0.1), 
                        random.seed = 1234,
                        verbose = FALSE)
srt$condition <- sce$condition
srt$sample <- sce$sample
srt$sorting <- sce$sorting
srt <- RunUMAP(srt, n.components = 10, dims = 1:25, reduction.key = "umap_pcs", verbose = FALSE)
